node.text:
In this video go over what luminosity masks are, how we can we can create them manually and with the Pro Panel, and how we can apply them in our images to take our editing to the next level.

This video cut off at 15 min to watch the last few min or watch in HD on a bigger screen, visit my YouTube. Link in bio. 

To get the Pro Panel use the link in bio
